About the game: The Runaway Feijoão is a casual indie game inspired by the old Tom & Jerry (NES) game, bringing you to difficult and addictive gameplay through the human digestive system. Can you find the way out? Key Features: 15 Levels. Enemies are parts of the human body and rice?. Play until you escape through the human digestive system and sewer.
